'''Renewal''' erased a being's memory. The term was used by the [[Syndicat]] and the people of [[Phindar/Legends|Phindar]] to describe a process of [[Memory wipe/Legends|memory wiping]] that they used as a cruel means of punishment.

As a young [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]], [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] was subjected to renewing, However he was able to keep his memory intact through the use of his [[The Force/Legends|Force]] abilities. It was said among the [[Phindian/Legends|Phindians]] that some strong-minded beings could resist being renewed.

It was also a process the [[Ssi-ruuvi]] used to cleanse a [[Human/Legends|Human]] brain of any resistance before the implementation of new thoughts and ideas.

